room_title: Escape room "Aunt Elna's Inheritance" by Escape Games NM in Aztec
room_description: Your cousins are looking to steal their mom's inheritance and even placed Elna in a retirement home to get rid of her faster. She's desperate to save her most prized possession, so she came to you, her favorite nieces and nephews. Help her retrieve the secret stash, and the inheritance is yours!
